metadata.name: envisage
metadata.description:
As I finished rendering my architecture work, I felt silent for a bit. 

I've created tons of architecture, painted some landscapes, created my own character sketches. But this thought, it never came to my mind, not until now.  I wonder, what does it feel like to live in my creation? I hope someday, I get to reside or be in my art.

How nice would that feel. 

-

2388 x 1668 px
